    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/20f949538cf5391b4b008a7905bd394f.avif?t=1762632110\" width=320 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the chilling world of paranormal investigation. Gather crucial information from a haunted location using specialized equipment, all while staying one step ahead of the ghost. Experience the psychological horror alone or in a team of up to 4 players. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/2ddfe9f89b552b2842a6e5268a47d317.avif?t=1762632110\" width=320 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Danger is around every corner inside the haunted location. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/1ee7f8c7424632825554a0e0dd55d978.poster.avif?t=1762632110\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/1ee7f8c7424632825554a0e0dd55d978.webm?t=1762632110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't turn your back on your teammates as certain ghost types can take over their body. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/dd5cf6ac899833155f8129e9f65ffc25.poster.avif?t=1762632110\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/dd5cf6ac899833155f8129e9f65ffc25.webm?t=1762632110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/51a8d5ed1369ce1a5abe704ed6ea9a41.avif?t=1762632110\" width=320 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware who you trust as some ghosts can mimic the voice and appearance of investigators. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/8a9ef2ffa378bf4877b78711b6e576f5.poster.avif?t=1762632110\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/8a9ef2ffa378bf4877b78711b6e576f5.webm?t=1762632110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/4f9b1e4419d9eee551d8d24522dfb987.avif?t=1762632110\" width=320 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience terrifying hallucinations that distort your reality. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/3ddbc7979ee85a6b19238f5b701f463c.poster.avif?t=1762632110\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/3ddbc7979ee85a6b19238f5b701f463c.webm?t=1762632110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/ce0c38b125e2dc89e5a4c8a2b98e8fff.avif?t=1762632110\" width=320 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/6e3ea66b91f58fb2407512b06b4f2485.poster.avif?t=1762632110\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/6e3ea66b91f58fb2407512b06b4f2485.webm?t=1762632110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Express yourself through your character's appearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select from multiple options and sliders to create your ideal look.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coordinating outfits with teammates or stand out as the investigator with your own style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/eeec3675b29a202c3a18d0dd4bfca623.avif?t=1762632110\" width=320 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the 37 ghost types and the abilities that set them apart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a variety of exhilarating hunts that will test your survival skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in proximity-based communication with the ethereal realm by speaking into your microphone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191690/extras/b67d1b4713b79a883713e13bc6ad5439.avif?t=1762632110\" width=320 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ectoplasm is a living, breathing horror experience that will evolve over time. Expect regular updates that bring new maps, items, mechanics, and even ghost types to ensure the terror never grows stale. The supernatural world is vast, and your journey into the unknown has only just begun. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face your fears and survive the relentless onslaught of the supernatural in Ectoplasm. Are you ready to walk the thin line between life and death?</p>",
